For today I will be doing a 1-minute review on the highly acclaimed psychological thriller namely - Mirai Nikki (The Future Diary). Let's Go!\
STORY : 6\
This 26-episode ride starts off with a bang from the very first episode. As this is a thriller it should be standard-fare to expect twists every now and again so you will need to pay close attention to the plot, but not that it becomes an emotional burden at any stage. However, there are various plot holes and they are impossible to miss as your mind is always in 5th gear looking for that extra piece of info.\
