Enjoyment 8/10: Here is my biggest problem with the show, the series atmosphere felt really weak at some points, like i wanted to see more plot twists(however there are definitely some major ones), and it felt as if it was being told more as some normal fantasy instead of some trippy psychological thriller. But besides that I loves almost everything about it. Good character development, good art, interesting characters etc. \
