CHARACTER 10- The character development is really amazing and maybe that's one of the many reasons why I liked the anime. Especially, Yuki's character gravely changed after his parent's death and made him more like Yuno which I enjoyed a lot. Even his scumbag father really had a character in him. And Yuno was outstanding, how easy it was for her to cut their necks and stab their stomachs and I really liked how she acts when she snaps out and gains her sanity. She is completely unpredictable! \
