Storyline&Characters:\
The storyline in combination with the characters really make the anime. The plot is great and can be (for some people) disturbing. However that doesn't change the fact that Mirai Nikki is still an awesome anime to watch.\
In my opinion there is not much character development (You'll have to see for yourself what changes)\
