    So... I've completed this anime today and I just want to write a short review about it. I'm not really into this thriller genre but I've found this one quite interesting so I've decided to watch it. I found that like after the 3rd episode it becomes also a little addictive. I had all the time a feeling that it's really similar to Deadman Wonderland, which I really disliked, but luckily this turned out to be a lot better for me.\
